OL,3,CFormer Corrie star Rupert Hill to take
OL,4,Cover Chorlton pub
OL,6,FRupert Hill has promised to "unlock
OL,7,Fthe potential" of an iconic pub he's
OL,8,Fhad his sights set on "for years."
OL,10,FThe former star, known for playing
OL,11,FJamie Baldwin, will be taking over The
OL,12,FLloyds Pub in alongside long-time
OL,13,Fbusiness partner Jonny Booth.
OL,15,FThe pair have found success in recent
OL,16,Fyears revitalising forgotten or
OL,17,Funcared for historic pubs across ,
OL,18,Fincluding The Castle Hotel and
OL,19,FGullivers.
