OL,3,CFormer Corrie star Rupert Hill to take
OL,4,Cover Chorlton pub
OL,6,FRupert says: "'From day one, we've
OL,7,Ffound this shared passion for taking
OL,8,Fweary and underperforming pubs with
OL,9,Fbags of potential and breathing new
OL,10,Flife into them, bringing them back
OL,11,Finto the community, creating places
OL,12,Fthat people love to be in.
OL,14,F"It's always felt like a worthwhile
OL,15,Fendeavour."
OL,17,FThis latest venture will see the
OL,18,Freturn of the pair to Chorlton, many
OL,19,Fyears after their joint venture, The
OL,20,FParlour, became one of their first big
OL,21,Fhospitality success stories.
