OL,3,CFormer Corrie star Rupert Hill to take
OL,4,Cover Chorlton pub
OL,6,FHowever, Rupert and Jonny admitted
OL,7,Fthat while they have found success in
OL,8,Fthe past, this latest attempt to
OL,9,Frevitalise an iconic pub comes with a
OL,10,Ffresh set of challenges.
OL,12,FJonny said: "We'll be taking a
OL,13,Fcautious approach to any kind of food
OL,14,Foffer given that, in the current
OL,15,Fclimate, food has become such a
OL,16,Fdifficult thing to profitably deliver,
OL,17,Fwith loads of our old favourite's
OL,18,Ffalling by the wayside.J"We're looking
OL,19,Finto a few potential options from
OL,20,Frotating pop ups to something akin to
OL,21,Fthe coffee shop model.
