OL,3,CFormer Corrie star Rupert Hill to take
OL,4,Cover Chorlton pub
OL,6,FFor their takeover of The Lloyds Pub,
OL,7,Fthey've teamed up with JW Lees Brewery
OL,8,Fto transform the venue and bring it in
OL,9,Fline with their other sites.
OL,11,FJonny says: "We've been after this
OL,12,Fsite for years and I've finally
OL,13,Fconvinced Lees to move it back out of
OL,14,Ftheir managed estate and give it to
OL,15,Fus!"
OL,17,FThey are also planning to change its
OL,18,Fname from The Llolyds to its original
OL,19,Fname when it first opened back in 1870
OL,20,Fon Wilbraham Road - Lloyd & Platt.
