OL,3,CFormer Corrie star Rupert Hill to take
OL,4,Cover Chorlton pub
OL,6,FA major part of the refurb will be to
OL,7,Fchange the function room into an
OL,8,Fevents space "worthy of the city
OL,9,Fcentre", playing host to live music,
OL,10,Fcinema, literary, comedy and DJ events.
OL,12,FThe pub will also offer a non-
OL,13,Falcoholic menu, after both owners
OL,14,Frecently stopped drinking.
OL,16,FRupert said: "Both Jonny and I are now
OL,17,Fnon-drinkers so we'll be working to
OL,18,Fbring a great Alcohol-free offer,
OL,19,Fevents and fun activities to welcome
OL,20,Fall the non-drinkers among us."
